<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Your PixiCred Application is Approved!</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px;">
  <h1 style="color: #27ae60;">Congratulations! Your Application is Approved</h1>
  <p>Dear {{firstName}} {{lastName}},</p>
  <p>We are pleased to inform you that your PixiCred credit card application has been approved.</p>

  <table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin: 16px 0;">
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; font-weight: bold;">Credit Limit</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">${{creditLimit}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; font-weight: bold;">Opening Balance</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">$500.00</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; font-weight: bold;">First Payment Due Date</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">{{paymentDueDate}}</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <h2 style="margin-top: 24px;">Account Setup Code</h2>
  <p>
    Your Account Setup Code is: <strong style="font-size: 1.2em; letter-spacing: 2px;">{{accountId}}</strong>
  </p>
  <p>
    To create your portal password and access your account online, visit
    <a href="{{baseUrl}}/setup">{{baseUrl}}/setup</a>
    and enter your Account Setup Code.
  </p>

  <p>Welcome to PixiCred!</p>
  <p>Sincerely,<br />The PixiCred Team</p>
</body>
</html>
